{"tid":776140,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［中國最中堅盟友］巴基斯坦發生自殺式炸彈襲擊，針對中國企業？ 3中國人受傷","createTime":"2018-08-11T18:10:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-11T23:54:33.000Z","uid":46245,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c295243091f5c6c44d8b52f706f3d93da0ee2493","tid":776140,"uid":46245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T18:10:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180811/58551634\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180811%2F58551634&d=7TYmk9QvXJAnk%2BOrP1FAacVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=5615bf88\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180811%2F58551634&h=7c8ae4d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180811/58551634</a><br />\n<br />\n（新增內容）路透社今日引述巴基斯坦警方報道，指西部城鎮達爾本丁（Dalbandin）一架載有中國工人的巴士發生自殺式炸彈襲擊，造成5人受傷，當中包括3名中國公民。當地的俾路支分離主義分子已承認責任。<br />\n<br />\n當地警方指，當巴士快到達目的地時，有人提住裝有爆炸物的行李並引爆炸彈。目前，中國駐巴基斯坦使館尚未證實有關消息。<br />\n<br />\n另據中國之聲消息，有卡拉奇總領使館人員表示，受傷的3名中國人都是中冶集團資源開發有限公司在當地的員工，其中2人在爆炸中被玻璃劃傷，另一人輕傷，全部都沒生命危險。<br />\n<br />\n路透社/環球網/澎湃新聞網"},{"pid":"b4eb6b7356adb117ab66a9eec2162a14117cf657","tid":776140,"uid":41545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T21:13:51.000Z","msg":"巴基斯坦：支那無仲未課夠金呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1b8cbe79de948d4b61597281297e1a0e99ec067","tid":776140,"uid":41545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T21:14:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴基斯坦：支那你仲未課夠金呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"365f3410512aecb698803bd37c7d5f5f3c6d0d57","tid":776140,"uid":71768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T23:54:33.000Z","msg":"咁炸彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 定炮丈"}]}